@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zludbo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.07)) / ((tmp + 0.33 + v0 + 0.97) + (v2 + 0.75 - v1 + 0.06)))
    v0 = 0.84
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = wp.exp(0.16)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.54))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.07)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.30) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
